==Introduction==
初期機動部隊の航空打撃力の中核となった名艦上攻撃機、通称「九七艦攻」。<br>
旧式化した同機を強化改修、改良調整を施した機上電探空六号改及び夜間作戦装備を搭載したif改修夜間艦上攻撃機、試製三号艦攻戊型、通称「九七式艦攻改」です。<br>
国産の実用夜間攻撃機、その最初の翼をぜひ提督の艦隊に！

''The Type 97 Torpedo Bomber was a renowned plane that formed the core of the attack wings of the early carrier task forces.''<br>
''The Type 97 is an older plane model that has been upgraded and equipped with the Type 6 Airborne Radar and fitted out for night operations.''<br>
''This "what if" night bomber remodel of the Type 97 Torpedo Bomber Kai is designated "Prototype No. 3 Model E". Please use the first domestic night bomber in your fleet, Admirals!''

